LevitateOS License Information
===============================

This project contains multiple components with different licenses:


1. LEVITATEOS SOURCE CODE
-------------------------
License: MIT OR Apache-2.0 (dual-licensed)
Copyright (c) 2024-2026 LevitateOS Contributors

All LevitateOS source code is dual-licensed under MIT and Apache-2.0.
You may choose either license. See LICENSE-MIT and LICENSE-APACHE.

This includes:
  - Rust crates (leviso, distro-spec, tools/*, etc.)
  - TypeScript packages (docs/content, docs/tui, docs/website)
  - Python code (llm-toolkit)

Contributions are accepted under the same dual license (inbound = outbound).


2. LEVITATEOS ISO - FEDORA BASE
-------------------------------
When you build a LevitateOS ISO, the resulting image contains Fedora packages
under various licenses:

  - Linux kernel           : GPL-2.0-only
  - systemd                : LGPL-2.1-or-later
  - GNU coreutils          : GPL-3.0-or-later
  - bash                   : GPL-3.0-or-later
  - util-linux             : GPL-2.0-or-later
  - NetworkManager         : GPL-2.0-or-later
  - GRUB2                  : GPL-3.0-or-later

Source packages available at: https://src.fedoraproject.org


3. ACORNOS ISO - ALPINE BASE
----------------------------
When you build an AcornOS ISO (Alpine-based variant), the resulting image
contains Alpine Linux packages under various licenses:

  - musl                   : MIT
  - busybox                : GPL-2.0
  - OpenRC                 : BSD-2-Clause
  - linux-lts              : GPL-2.0-only
  - apk-tools              : GPL-2.0
  - eudev                  : GPL-2.0-or-later
  - bash                   : GPL-3.0-or-later
  - coreutils              : GPL-3.0-or-later
  - GRUB                   : GPL-3.0-or-later

Alpine distribution itself is MIT licensed.
Source packages available at: https://pkgs.alpinelinux.org/packages
Source repositories: https://gitlab.alpinelinux.org


4. LINUX KERNEL SOURCE AVAILABILITY
-----------------------------------
LevitateOS uses the vanilla Linux kernel with configuration-only customization:

  - Version: 6.18.x-levitate (CONFIG_LOCALVERSION="-levitate")
  - Patches: None (vanilla kernel)
  - Configuration: leviso/kconfig

GPL-2.0 compliance is satisfied through:

  Upstream source:
    https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git

  LevitateOS mirror (with our config):
    https://github.com/LevitateOS/linux

No modifications to kernel source are distributed; only the kernel
configuration file (leviso/kconfig) which is MIT OR Apache-2.0 licensed.


5. RUST DEPENDENCIES
--------------------
LevitateOS depends on 268 external Rust crates, all under permissive licenses:

  - MIT OR Apache-2.0      : 168 crates
  - MIT only               : 46 crates
  - Apache-2.0 only        : 17 crates
  - Unicode-3.0            : 18 crates (unicode-* crates)
  - BSD variants           : 3 crates
  - CC0 / Unlicense        : 9 crates
  - MPL-2.0                : 3 crates

No copyleft licenses (GPL, AGPL, SSPL) are present in Rust dependencies.

Verification: Run `cargo deny check licenses` from the repository root.
Configuration: deny.toml


6. THIRD-PARTY MODELS
---------------------
License: Apache-2.0
Copyright (c) 2025 Hugging Face

The SmolLM3-3B language model used for the AI installer is Apache 2.0 licensed.
See LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt for the full license text.
Source: https://huggingface.co/HuggingFaceTB/SmolLM3-3B


7. DISTRIBUTION OBLIGATIONS
---------------------------
If you distribute LevitateOS or AcornOS images, you must:

  a) Include this LICENSE file or equivalent notices
  b) Provide access to source code for GPL/LGPL components
  c) Preserve copyright notices

Source availability for GPL/LGPL compliance:

  Fedora packages:    https://src.fedoraproject.org
  Alpine packages:    https://pkgs.alpinelinux.org/packages
  Linux kernel:       https://github.com/LevitateOS/linux
  SmolLM3 model:      https://huggingface.co/HuggingFaceTB/SmolLM3-3B


8. FULL LICENSE TEXTS
---------------------
See the LICENSES/ directory:

  LICENSES/MIT.txt           LevitateOS code, musl
  LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt    LevitateOS code, SmolLM3 model
  LICENSES/GPL-2.0.txt       Linux kernel, busybox, util-linux, apk-tools
  LICENSES/GPL-3.0.txt       GNU coreutils, bash, GRUB
  LICENSES/LGPL-2.1.txt      systemd
  LICENSES/BSD-2-Clause.txt  OpenRC
